* ''[[The Bing Crosby – Chesterfield Show]]''<ref>{{cite web|last1=Pairpoint|first1=Lionel|title=And Here's Bing!|url=http://www.bingmagazine.co.uk/bingmagazine/chesterfield.htm|website=BING magazine|publisher=International Club Crosby|accessdate=December 24, 2015}}</ref> (1949–1952, CBS), 30 minutes weekly.
* ''[[The Bing Crosby Show for General Electric]]''<ref>{{cite web|last1=Pairpoint|first1=Lionel|title=And Here's Bing!|url=http://www.bingmagazine.co.uk/bingmagazine/ge.htm|website=BING magazine|publisher=International Club Crosby|accessdate=December 24, 2015}}</ref> (1952–1954, CBS), 30 minutes weekly.
* ''[[The Bing Crosby Show (1954–1956)]]''<ref>{{cite web|last1=Pairpoint|first1=Lionel|title=And Here's Bing!|url=http://www.bingmagazine.co.uk/bingmagazine/final.htm#bcshow|website=BING magazine|publisher=International Club Crosby|accessdate=December 24, 2015}}</ref> (CBS), 15 minutes, 5 nights a week.
